</p>

</div>
<div id="fn" class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#GEWN-03-03-02-0196-fn-0001-ptr" id="GEWN-03-03-02-0196-fn-0001">1</a>

   <p>On this date GW gave a warrant to Joseph Bacon for $286 21/72 or 85.17.9 to reimburse Trumbull for the expenses of Penet and Pliarne (account of warrants signed, 10 Sept. 177512 Aug. 1776, <span class="ref-rep" title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover ] header=[]  body=[ U.S. Library of Congress, George Washington Papers, Washington, D.C. ]">DLC:GW</span>).</p>

</div>
